        <list id="id8721404" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>It will <emphasis effect="bold">CONVERGE</emphasis> light beams towards a fixed point, the <emphasis effect="bold">FOCUS.</emphasis></item>
          <item>Other mirrors may be <emphasis effect="bold">CONVEX</emphasis>.</item>
          <item>They will cause light beams to <emphasis effect="bold">DIVERGE</emphasis> (spread apart)</item>
          <item>This scales down the image.</item>
          <item>An application of this is evident in the rear view mirror of a motor car or in winged mirrors.</item>
